{"word":"G141 - αἱρετικός - hairetikós - hahee-ret-ee-kos' - Heretic","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">αἱρετικός</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">hairetikós</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hahee-ret-ee-kos'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Heretic</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"வேதப்புரட்டன் - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"1. fitted or able to take or choose a thing"},{"paragraph":"2. schismatic, factious, a follower of false doctrine"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From the same as <a href=\"#/G140 - αἱρετίζω - hairetízō - hahee-ret-id'-zo/140\">G140</a>; a <i>schismatic</i>. (&ldquo;heretic&rdquo; is the Greek word itself.): - heretic [the Greekord itself].</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1243/1243\">G1243</a>, <a href=\"#/G1244/1244\">G1244</a>, <a href=\"#/G138/138\">G138</a>, <a href=\"#/G139/139\">G139</a>, <a href=\"#/G140/140\">G140</a>, <a href=\"#/G141/141\">G141</a>"}]}